      "rationale": "Standard NAFEMS benchmark problems covering linear elastic stress states were solved with the same solver settings used in the pedicle screw model. All results within 1% of published reference solutions, confirming correct code implementation."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
