      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus drawn from certified material test reports for the production lot. Screw and rod dimensions measured on three representative samples per nominal size using calibrated CMM. Monte Carlo uncertainty propagation (500 samples) quantified combined input uncertainty contribution to each QoI."
