      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 fixture offset (50 mm). Only one loading condition evaluated due to resource constraints. Achieved level 2 falls below required level 3; this gap is noted in the credibility summary and accepted by the decision authority given that the single condition is the most clinically relevant worst-case scenario."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
