      "rationale": "Fixture geometry digitized from ASTM F1717 standard drawings and replicated in the FEA boundary conditions. Spherical joint at inferior fixture and prescribed displacement at superior fixture match experimental setup. Set-screw torque preload (4 Nm) included as initial contact pressure. Equivalency confirmed by comparing reaction forces at fixture attachment points."
    },
