      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three primary performance metrics specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance for spinal pedicle screw systems. These QoIs directly inform the regulatory submission and clinical risk assessment."
